data.description: Discover the essence of Peachtree City living with this impeccable two-story residence situated in the sought-after Chadsworth at Ashton Reserve subdivision. Set within a serene cul-de-sac, this home is a harmonious blend of suburban tranquility and the conveniences that come with its close proximity to Peachtree's signature 100+ miles of multiuse pathways.  Natural light bathes the interiors, beautifully illuminating the freshly painted walls and spacious living areas. The heart of this home is undeniably its state-of-the-art kitchen, replete with pristine granite countertops, a central island, contemporary white cabinetry, and brand-new stainless-steel appliances. Complementing the kitchen's elegance is the newly fitted cabinet hardware.  Featuring four well-appointed bedrooms, this home offers ample space for both families and guests. The master suite is a testament to luxury with its double vanity and an expansive custom-built walk-in closet. The main bathroom exudes modern sophistication, spotlighting a new freestanding bath and a spacious walk-in shower. Not to be outdone, the second bathroom has been beautifully updated, mirroring the home’s commitment to elegance and functionality.  An elegant separate dining room, easily accessible from both the kitchen and the foyer entrance, offers a dedicated space for intimate dinners and grand feasts alike. Those seeking versatility will appreciate the office on the main level, which can be effortlessly transformed into a fifth bedroom. Further enhancing the home’s practicality is the conveniently located second-floor laundry room, making chores a breeze and providing utmost convenience to all family members.  The property's outdoor spaces are equally inviting. The extended patio in the private backyard sets the stage for gatherings, while the newly installed light fittings enrich the ambiance as day transitions to night.  In terms of location, 512 Merrill Ln is unparalleled. Less than 2 miles away lie a diverse array of amenities, from charming local eateries to bustling retail hubs and entertainment venues like movie theaters. Additionally, the accessibility to Costco, Sam's Club, and Interstate 85 makes daily errands and commutes an absolute breeze.  The nearby golf courses, such as the prestigious Planterra Ridge Golf Club, Braelinn, and Flat Creek, beckon golf lovers to test their skills on immaculately maintained fairways. Tee off at Planterra Ridge for a challenging round of golf, set against a backdrop of rolling greens and serene lakes. Whether you're a seasoned pro or a novice, the courses around Peachtree City offer an unparalleled golfing experience.  Tennis courts are always ready for a friendly match, and the refreshing community pools offer a welcome respite during the scorching Georgia summers.  There are a plethora of parks and playgrounds, perfect for picnics, outdoor games, and creating cherished memories. But what truly sets Peachtree City apart is its network of walking and biking trails. These paths, intertwined with the community, make it easy to explore the area, offering a unique and scenic way to get around town.  Just a short drive away, Lake McIntosh beckons with its serene waters, perfect for boating, fishing, or a tranquil lakeside picnic. Hikers can lose themselves in the beauty of Line Creek Nature Area or Flat Creek Nature Preserve, where the rustling leaves and singing birds provide a soothing backdrop to each step.  Bird watchers will find their paradise in Peachtree City, where the rich biodiversity ensures a never-ending spectacle of colorful avian residents. Grab your binoculars or camera and a field guide and prepare to be amazed.  Finally, this property is located in an award-winning school district. Kedron Elementary, Booth Middle, and McIntosh High service this residence, all facilitated by a convenient school bus route close-by.  512 Merrill Ln in Peachtree City is not just a house; it's an invitation to a lifesty
